Troubleshooting Tips
Server won't start:

Check if port 8080 is already in use: netstat -tlnp | grep 8080
Verify Python dependencies: pip3 list | grep -E "flask|requests"
Check logs for errors: tail -f logs/decoy-server.log
No traffic being generated:

Verify traffic obfuscator is running: ps aux | grep traffic_obfuscator
Check network connectivity: curl http://localhost:8080/health
Review obfuscator logs for errors
Logs not being created:

Ensure logs directory exists and is writable
Check file permissions: ls -la logs/
Verify logging configuration in scripts
